description.narrative: The office continued to invest in promoting quality evaluative evidence for programming. Despite COVID-19, evaluative efforts of the office have not stopped and the Costed Evaluation Plan is still being followed. The Country Led Mine Risk Education evaluation is ongoing and the Country Led VAC Action Plan evaluation is in its contracting stage. In addition to evaluations, evaluation has stepped up to support the Covid-19 response by carrying out a behavioral change monitoring of RCCE, and through this supporting outcome level monitoring. National evaluation capacity development has also been reinforced, through training of government officials on evaluation and M&E systems. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:21/08/2020
